data.description: Welcome to 254 Harrisonville Rd in Mullica Hill, New Jersey! This home offers the convenience of main level living with all three bedrooms located on the first floor. Situated on a vast lot spanning over 2.5 acres, Step inside and be greeted by a spacious and inviting living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones. The kitchen has been updated with sleek stainless steel appliances, beautiful countertops, and ample storage space. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a cozy dining area that overlooks the expansive backyard. The main level of this home features a luxurious master suite complete with a full en-suite bathroom. The new home owner will want to customize to their liking.  Two additional bedrooms on the main level share a full bathroom, providing comfort and convenience for all residents. With all bedrooms located on the first floor, this home offers the perfect setup for easy and accessible living. Outside, the large lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, and enjoying the serene natural surroundings. Whether you're hosting a barbecue, playing with your pets, or simply unwinding after a long day, this backyard, although needs work, provides the ideal setting. Conveniently located in the heart of Mullica Hill, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options.  The property needs work and is being offered in  "as-is" condition.
